# Understanding the Challenge
By default, provisioners that fil will also cause the terraform apply itself to tail.

This will lead to resource being tained and we have to re-create the resource

# Basics of On Failure Setting
The on_failer setting can be used to change the default behaviour.

Values |
continue   : Ignore the error and continue with creation pr destruction
fail       : Raise an error and strop applying (the default behavior). If this is creatiion provisioner, taint the resource.